  "title": "QUANTITY SURVEYOR",
  "description": "<ol><li>Contract administration of selected projects.</li><li>Preparation of monthly valuations for progress payments to the Main Contractor, Nominated Sub-Contractors or Nominated Suppliers.</li><li>Measurement, valuation, negotiation and agreement with the Contractor / Sub-Contractor of all variations to the Contract.</li><li>Preparation of regular cost reconcillation statements of the project showing payments to-date & projected final cost.</li><li>Attendance of site meeting and virtual meeting.</li><li>Preparation & agreement of final accounts for the project.</li></ol>",
